{"data":[{"date":"10:14 20/08","title":"HLV Inter Milan b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/luciano-spalletti-phat-bieu-sau-tran-sassuolo-10-inter-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Luciano Spalletti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Serie A.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sassuolo</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sassuolo \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Serie A 2018/19, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Inter tung ra 10 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 3 l\u00e0 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSassuolo t\u1ecf ra hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda Inter (5) song 3 l\u00e0 tr\u00fang c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n v\u00e0 1 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. C\u00fa ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Domenico Berardi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Sassuolo gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0, t\u1ea1m v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH Serie A v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y Inter xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 18/20 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luciano Spalletti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luciano Spalletti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/luciano-spalletti-phat-bieu-sau-tran-sassuolo-10-inter-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Luciano Spalletti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Spalletti kh\u00f4ng lo \u00e2u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Luciano Spalletti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1 ra. \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3\u201d, Spalletti n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Sau b\u00e0n thua, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Sassuolo ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nInter s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eeda sai khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Torino t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Serie A \u0111\u00eam ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi (26/8).<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sassuolo-10-inter-milan-man-ra-quan-tham-hoa-cua-ung-vien-176-194869.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/sassuolo-10-inter-milan-man-ra-quan-tham-hoa-cua-ung-vien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sassuolo-10-inter-milan-man-ra-quan-tham-hoa-cua-ung-vien-176-194869.html\">Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan: M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sassuolo, Mauro Icardi thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Inter b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5688","checkdouble":"194866"},{"date":"09:59 20/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/truyen-thong-nhat-ban-nhan-xet-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c sau khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<br />\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng nhau, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \"chung k\u1ebft\" c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D. Quang H\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/truyen-thong-nhat-ban-nhan-xet-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng B/E/F \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/8.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec<br />\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. T\u1edd Hochi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i: \"Sau hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1\".<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Soccer King \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua: \"\u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thua b\u00e0n khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m\".<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Nikkan Sports \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng: \"C\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maeda l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nguy hi\u1ec3m. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong hi\u1ec7p hai mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\".<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Malaysia.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-chi-quoc-te-noi-gi-khi-olympic-viet-nam-da-bai-nhat-ban-168-194847.html\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-len-tieng-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-cua-viet-nam-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194845.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hung-dung-chinh-thuc-mat-asiad-2018-168-194833.html\">N\u00d3NG: H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5687","checkdouble":"194871"},{"date":"10:52 20/08","title":"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, song g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chi-63-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-quyet-tam-mua-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar, Mbappe v\u00e0 Hazard l\u00e0 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng cho Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u00ec Hazard l\u1ea1i cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karim Benzema, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/hlv-psg-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-edinson-cavani-197-192355.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Thomas Tuchel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Cavani</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u00eda PSG t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn, song Real Madrid v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-PSG-len-63-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Edinson Cavani l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng Cavani s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Benzema, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Napoli.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Cavani, nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Morata hay Lewandowski \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu PSG kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5686","checkdouble":"194880"},{"date":"11:19 20/08","title":"Gareth Bale n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga c\u1ee7a Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bale c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 20 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Getafe tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng Dani Carvajal. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 51, Gareth Bale \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 b\u1eb1ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga. Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh tham gia.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nacho Fernandez th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real. C\u00f2n Bale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o Bale. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf ph\u00eda sau Bale v\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Cavani l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale-180-194865.html\">Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-real-madrid-vs-getafe-20-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194857.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5685","checkdouble":"194887"},{"date":"10:11 20/08","title":"Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Scholes \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Pogba sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi Man United b\u1ecb Brighton \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-3, Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 Brighton l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. \u0110\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Brighton thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1t khao h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean b\u1edfi v\u00ec th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Scholes cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Paul Scholes cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Pogba \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mong l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ai \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ebft l\u1ea1i sai l\u1eddi Pogba. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean t\u1ef1 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec c\u00f4ng khai nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. N\u1ebfu th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m cho n\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n HLV hay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Amex. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec th\u00ec Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o ra. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. Sai l\u1ea7m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Odl Trafford v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-mu-phan-ung-cuc-soc-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194875.html\">NHM MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kho-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-du-suc-vao-top-4-172-194867.html\">MU kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o Top 4</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5684","checkdouble":"194879"},{"date":"10:26 20/08","title":"Morata: \"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League trong n\u0103m 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u1ea5y l\u00ean. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u1edf Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 La Liga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Morata trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Arsenal h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Morata quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m x\u00f3a h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u1eb7c Italia. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng </em><em>v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t t\u00f4i m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng cho ch\u00ednh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n mua nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a b\u00e9 l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111i h\u1ecdc \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac ch\u1ee9. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Chelsea n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Gi\u1edd thi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e9n nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-mot-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal-du-suc-dung-trong-doi-hinh-chelsea-172-194868.html\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-kovacic-noi-gi-sau-man-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194861.html\">T\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5683","checkdouble":"194881"},{"date":"10:49 20/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Man United ch\u1ec9 mang v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u1eeba \u00fd HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng Dalot non kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay Grant l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c CLB Premier League, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Gary-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-MU-va-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u1ea1i Premier League, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Brighton \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Mourinho trong mua s\u1eafm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sau khi Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, Neville n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports. \u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3/4 l\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho thu\u00ea n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 c\u00f2n dang d\u1edf. M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u. Nh\u1eefng David Moyes v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Louis van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 chi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 700 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00eam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 CLB n\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n khi c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh-172-194297.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho-172-194167.html\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t: \u0110\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5682","checkdouble":"194883"},{"date":"11:35 20/08","title":"Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves c\u1ee7a Wolves, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man xanh, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri \u1edf Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Man-City-muon-mua-Ruben-Neves-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Jorginho, Man City \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Aaron Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef Ramsey th\u00ec Lazio h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Pep \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-de-bruyne-172-194571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kevin de Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> 3 th\u00e1ng c\u00f2n David Silva tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean bu\u1ed9c Pep ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, Ruben Neves l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pep quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves c\u1ee7a Wolves, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City muon mua Ruben Neves\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ruben Neves l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Wolves, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.\u00a0M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 khi\u1ebfn Pep \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Man xanh chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Man City chi ra l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ruben Neves l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cAndrea Pirlo m\u1edbi\u201d, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5681","checkdouble":"194884"},{"date":"10:47 20/08","title":"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Brighton \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Amex khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man United c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn qua 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Bailly &ndash; Lindelof\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104406-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Bailly \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 Brighton c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Bailly v\u1edbi Pascal Gross \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty, \u00edt ph\u00fat sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Lukaku. S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a Bailly \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn Man United b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng pha ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man United t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Bailly l\u00e0 Lindelof c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 Glenn Murray c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Pascal Gross tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e1 ngay \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial\" title=\"Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104515-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martial ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf Sanchez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda n\u00e0o l\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. S\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a Shaw c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n b\u1edfi Marouane Fellaini. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Sanchez ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t khi anh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Ashley Young\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Young\" title=\"Young\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104521-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Young kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i Nga. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Young v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 33 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Khi l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Young c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng \u1edf trong nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Young l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Young l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu Mourinho mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9nh sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2&nbsp;MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu-172-194883.html\">Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194878.html\">Anthony Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5680","checkdouble":"194886"},{"date":"08:46 20/08","title":"Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan: M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/sassuolo-10-inter-milan-man-ra-quan-tham-hoa-cua-ung-vien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sassuolo, Mauro Icardi thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Inter b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 v\u00e0i ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Radja Nainggolan, Keita Balde... v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim, tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, tham v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus trong su\u1ed1t 7 n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Sassuolo th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 C\u0110V San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, n\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 1 c\u00e1i t\u00e1t cho s\u1ef1 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Spalletti.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/180820_054210_81.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sassuolo, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef Perisic tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, trong khi t\u00e2n binh Nainggolan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Nerazzurri \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, Inter tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n \u1edf trung l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a Sassuolo. V\u00ec th\u1ebf g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Spalletti \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec Sassuolo l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 27, Miranda bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1eb3ng tay ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 Domenico Berardi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1, \u0111\u01b0a Sassuolo v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 h\u1edf t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 cho Inter trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Inter bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tung ra nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Hi\u1ec7p 1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n cho Sassuolo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Spalletti l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Keita Balde v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Inter kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter g\u00e2y ra c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Sassuolo c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. C\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Consigli c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Perisic, Icardi \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Inter tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n Nerazzurri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n tham v\u1ecdng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5679","checkdouble":"194869"},{"date":"07:28 20/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 sau c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n \u0111em v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean 30 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real, khi Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00e3 thay nhau l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea7y K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u1ed5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1c quan tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a CR7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bale3-3160-1534720660.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Real Madrid v\u1eabn \u0111ang 's\u1ed1ng kh\u1ecfe' th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Bale \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real, l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111ang d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale, ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Bale \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho Real sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Gatafe.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, Bale c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t cho Real. Ngay ph\u00fat&nbsp;th\u1ee9 7, ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales tung c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Soria m\u1edbi c\u1ee9u cho Getafe kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua. Ph\u00fat 16, Bale \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Marcelo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bale2-7123-1534720660.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Getafe \u0111\u00e3 rung l\u00ean. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Gareth Bale. C\u00fa t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i b\u0103ng ra ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm t\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo, Bale \u0111ang l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Bale ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Getafe ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau Cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh. HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Carvajal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 20 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu v\u1edbi Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, Getafe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Real. Tr\u1ea3i qua 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Geta lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid vs Getafe\" title=\"Real Madrid vs Getafe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/15347154163333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008/09 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Getafe \u0111\u00e3 9 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 Real, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-3-3 c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt lo ng\u1ea1i khi nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111ang \u1edf b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, m\u1ea3ng mi\u1ebfng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 bi\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf ph\u00eda&nbsp; trong l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u00f3a c\u00e1c mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lopetegui ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Courtois ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Keylor Navas v\u1eabn \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Lopetegui g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean anh \u0111\u1ec3 tin d\u00f9ng t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Courtois ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi: &quot;S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Courtois c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec h\u01a1n n\u1eefa cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Real song l\u00fac n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Navas.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span><br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/20/Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-2-0.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5678","checkdouble":"194863"},{"date":"08:55 20/08","title":"Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a La Liga. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Los Blancos c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid thay cho Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c ngay sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 khi \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Real \u0111\u1ee5ng Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 2-2 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos. Sang hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Saul Niguez v\u00e0 Koke ghi 2 b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 chung cu\u1ed9c cho Atletico c\u1ee7a Diego Simeone.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/HLV-Julen-Lopetegui-khen-ngoi-Gareth-Bale-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean La Liga b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Getafe tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui ng\u1ee3i ca Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe, HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui co man khoi dau suon se voi Real Madrid o La Liga 2018/19\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf La Liga 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4F385BC300000578-6076597-image-a-9_1534715056208.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian cho s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee9 3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi kh\u00f4ng cho h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-real-madrid-vs-getafe-20-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194857.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5677","checkdouble":"194865"},{"date":"19:56 19/08","title":"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Juventus tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-khien-juventus-tro-thanh-doi-bong-manh-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau bao ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ronaldo-juventus-chievo-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, n\u00f3i chung kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Chievo Verona \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Serie A 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u1ed9t Juventus c\u00f3 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cRonaldo gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi top \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i m\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho Champions League. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Serie A, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Napoli c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Inter Milan v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\">Chievo 2-3 Juventus: Ronaldo im \u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0 Serie A song Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2017 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Juventus...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5676","checkdouble":"194832"}]}